-- Siemens sets aside 3-digit million eur sum for job cuts
-- 
-- Thu Nov 8, 2012 7:07am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/11/08/us-siemens-savings-severance-idUSBRE8A70EF20121108

 

 BERLIN  (Reuters) - Siemens has already set aside a sum in the hundreds of millions of euros for severance payments as part of its new 6 billion-euro ($7.65 billion) cost-cutting program, its finance chief Joe Kaeser said. 
 (Reporting by  Maria Sheahan )